suite.doc:
A test suite with tests for SDWAN SINGLE CPE Solution. Topology:- ____________________________ | VersaDirector | |___________________________| | | | _____________|_______________ | WanCtrller1 | |____________________________| | | | | | | INTERNET/MPLS | | | |___ ______|__ ___|___ | | | | LAN1--+ CPE1 | | CPE2 +--LAN1 |________| |_______|
Testplan Goals:- 1. CHECK WAN INTERFACES STATUS. 2. CHECK BGP NEIGHBOR STATUS. 3. CHECK LAN ROUTE. 4. Ping Test. 5. IPERF Test.
